Chinese artist Yan Hong is a major influencer on one of China's most popular video platforms Bilibili. Her videos have wowed audiences from both home and abroad, including ones showing how to replicate a complete set of silver accessories of the Miao ethnic group. From researching information about ancient wears to finding suitable materials, her process of creationÂ hasn't always been trouble-free. Let's meet Yan, who shares with us her journey of reviving old crafts for the young generation.